(51, 33, 'Corundum-Mullit Products', 'color:red;font-weight:bold;', 'admin', 0, 1216228118, 1228504447, 69, '', 44, 1241617487, 0, 1, 0, '', '', 'With exellent performance in anti-high-tem-creep,anti-thermal attack and can be used between 1550℃-1700℃.\n\n\nDifferent specification can be provied based on the drawing by customers', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1),
