(54, 34, 'Alumina Bubble Brick (Type : AL-B and ML-B)', 'color:red;font-weight:bold;', 'admin', 0, 1216230187, 1228507437, 88, '', 33, 1216230187, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 'With excellent high-Temperature volume-stability, high refractoriness under load. For products with density of 1.5-1.7g/cm3, which widely used as lining brick for high-temperature tunnel kiln and drawer-type kiln, Max. working temperature up to 1800℃. For', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1),
