(21, 26, '<div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"upfiles/200805/19/1211210070_1.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"upfiles/200805/20/1211272787_1.jpg\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">用于生产艺术陶瓷、日用陶瓷、卫生陶瓷、电子材料、磁性材料等的辊道窑、隧道窑和梭式窑。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">耐火棚板的抗热震性能不错，而且高温强度、抗腐蚀性能都很好，所以可以用于烧成负载较重的艺术陶瓷、</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">日用陶瓷等。抗腐蚀性好，可以应用于烧成电子材料、磁性材料等复杂气氛条件下。使用温度可以达到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1300</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">度。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">本产品现正出口日本和韩国，客户反应良好。理化指标如下：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><o:p><font face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><s